{"tid":433542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然發覺自己宜家既狀態好恐怖","createTime":"2017-10-12T12:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T03:15:55.000Z","uid":100730,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"250b14675b44502fd1474fe395fe9276b99baa1d","tid":433542,"uid":100730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"頭先過馬路，見到係我前面個男人就黎比電車撞到，我竟然無反應，就咁睇住佢炒落去。好彩佢最後無事。<br />\n<br />\n見到其他人就黎出事，我唔係第一時間叫停，亦都唔係出手阻止，淨係下意識咁諗：「哦，有人要撞車啦。」之後反應返，先覺得自己嗰時既思想好得人驚。<br />\n<br />\n我開始覺得自己有事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4395cb2f6a90618796e3a74640c2ef0c437478e8","tid":433542,"uid":97634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"我有時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a988e84c77e0b6f6e4b8599ddcc7af70e957c6","tid":433542,"uid":56368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"我早幾日連自己差D有事都無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2690017ded00b25c22afc1ec2dc50f5c246dd145","tid":433542,"uid":56368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我早幾日連自己差D有事都無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人好似無哂腎上線素咁"},{"pid":"3d167c39cbad08173eabf77ed053bc00442e270a","tid":433542,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8027c88668312c41f8f733312c90c0d0828f23cc","tid":433542,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次有個人係我面前比車 HI到一HI掉抵左都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解會變到咁"},{"pid":"b6390772f50ab3f3056f7e3927253983d7455908","tid":433542,"uid":100730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"睇番今日有七單自殺新聞，我覺得香港已經病得好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90b7c8f370feec3273ddf7a8e0c5420bc86096b","tid":433542,"uid":10325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"其實唔關你事，係人見到都唔知點反應"},{"pid":"cc43d7c769a88a8d2b02851f5259448d9b137dac","tid":433542,"uid":100730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔關你事，係人見到都唔知點反應</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打開解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf46a29aa7a3f88f7355ea6f27f82d4d6a232df","tid":433542,"uid":97634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔關你事，係人見到都唔知點反應</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係我地反應遲鈍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b173ffe76b8e449e524a7e7d726720594121a593","tid":433542,"uid":91895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"我前幾晚都係咁....<br />\n等過馬路個陣突然好大雨 咁我就拎左把遮出來，但係捉唔實比風吹左出馬路<br />\n<br />\n當時有架巴士過緊來 但我竟然下意識係想衝出去執返把遮<br />\n<br />\n嚇到隔離個師奶即刻拉住我<br />\n<br />\n最後把遮當然比車碌到斷晒遮骨<br />\n我諗緊如果個陣隔離無人拉住可能斷骨嘅係我而唔係把遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6094f258d7a3ea92abaa1c9511b8864837bf0d8d","tid":433542,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"幾好 幾冷靜"},{"pid":"c0d5566d144a026a6e7675ec5f7862c59ae077f9","tid":433542,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"中學親人見個阿婆係樓上跌落黎 都無乜感覺 即刻報完驚番學校同囡囡吹水"},{"pid":"9db498117f17c1d01c4914ca20882c2fb82e5ffe","tid":433542,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"香港住太耐會冇左人性"},{"pid":"b85db7ca116846e1920ae5e26b3f5b0dbf3beddb","tid":433542,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔關你事，係人見到都唔知點反應</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係我地反應遲鈍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰個係你老母嘅話仲會唔會唔識反應呀？<br />\n成班麻木撚屌喺到自己呃自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a09505625e825c681a60f2b2913371c0291c50","tid":433542,"uid":42753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"日日收工顧自己都顧唔掂，思想經已麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3ae31bacdfbb6e11a3991287f948da9d62e0a2","tid":433542,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"我都係 見到有人掛住睇手機行咗出馬路 仲有車嚟緊 我竟然望住佢 而唔係叫佢<br />\n好彩佢自己醒一醒 如果唔係真係撞埋去"},{"pid":"61e4faf78e0df70f381a6ebef2cad8494a728258","tid":433542,"uid":10183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"上次比車撞，訓左落地轉兩個圈個頭撞左落電燈柱，第一個反應係起身返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da83c66947a21223fa80a9d2583bfe7f13babbeb","tid":433542,"uid":33661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 見到有人掛住睇手機行咗出馬路 仲有車嚟緊 我竟然望住佢 而唔係叫佢<br />\n好彩佢自己醒一醒 如果唔係真係撞埋去</blockquote><br />\n我係差啲比人撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 掛住睇手機連紅綠燈同有冇車都冇睇就行出去 聽到衝埋黎架的士呠我先醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccdb15b61945b5fc8a774e04d940c9857e20c89","tid":433542,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"成個環境令到人好麻木, 反應會遲鈍左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}